data.description: New to Market!  Step into luxury with this stunning 2626 sq ft Colonial, featuring a grand 2-story entry foyer that sets the tone for modern, luxury living. The open layout of this sun-drenched home is accentuated by vaulted and tray ceilings, creating an airy and inviting atmosphere throughout. Built in 2002, This home boasts 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, an abundance of storage space with organized closets everywhere and walk-in closets in the Primary bedroom. Enjoy the comfort of central air conditioning (1 yr old), gas heating (2019), and a kitchen equipped for gourmet cooking with a gas stove, new fridge, microwave & dishwasher). The basement is dry and finished, providing extra space for family fun. This residence is situated on a cul de sac with easy access to schools, town shops and restaurants. Part of North Shore School District (Glenwood Landing Elementary).  Taxes have never been grieved and are $18,430.81 with Basic STAR!
